author: Karen in Bowling Green KY
title: Karen in Bowling Green KY
text: I was very pleased with Biblio.com! I ordered several Baptist hymnals & they were reasonably priced AND in better shape than I expected! Very clean & packed well too! Thank you Biblio.com! I would DEFINITELY order again from you! I would DEFINITELY recommend you to others!
